Pagination Plugin
==================

A plugin that paginations an HTML ul or ol list element.


Usage
-----
$('#items').pagination();


Options
-------
You may change the global defaults by modifying the `$.fn.pagination.defaults` object.

$('#items').pagination({itemsPerPage: 10});

- **itemsPerPage**
  The number of list items to show per page. Default is 7.

- **pageLimit**
  The maximum number of pages before the navigation will be truncated. Default is 10.

- **midRange**
  Used to calculate the range for truncated navigation. Should be odd. Default is 7.



Files
-----

- **jquery-1.4.2.min.js**
  The version of jQuery used to create this plugin.

- **jquery.pagination.js**
  This plugin.

- **pagination.css**
  CSS styles that control the display of the paginated list and navigation.

- **pagination.html**
  Sample of paginated elements.
  
- **tests**
  Holds the plugin unit tests.

